"prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 誰知道。", "name": "客棧夥計"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "name2": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們這些新來的，已經不見掌櫃的用刀啦。想來也是，家大業大的，光靠酒樓就能在尚蜀站穩腳跟了吧。", "name": "街頭青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 掌櫃的到底怎麼用刀？", "name": "街頭青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "name2": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 掌櫃的這些年，用刀的次數實在不多。真要說，那就是砍瓜切菜，剁肉殺鱗。", "name": "客棧夥計"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 比起過去打打殺殺的日子，鄭掌櫃已經很久不以“傷人”為目的用刀了。", "name": "客棧夥計"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "name2": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......有一種江湖高人隱退的感覺？那現在他帶刀出去做啥？", "name": "街頭青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "name2": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 切菜吧。切了這麼久的菜了，掌櫃的也就會切切菜了。", "name": "客棧夥計"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "name2": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 無聊哦。", "name": "街頭青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "name2": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不然呢，切那麼多年菜，還能變厲害不成？", "name": "客棧夥計"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_npc_140_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes"