": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 年小姐果然知道些什麼。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#9$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 當然了。你和這玩意在一起的時間太久了。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 雖然尋常人類發現不了這隻酒盞的秘密，但是司歲台也好你也好都太不注意了點......", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......還是說，這也是你的考量......？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 年？", "name": "克洛絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不。我的事情先不提......那邊那位少年似乎想要積極發言？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......首先，我要求你們為夕的離開做出解釋。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 克洛絲小姐仍舊把你當作羅德島的一員，如此說來，在場三人，全部都與那羅德島有關。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 根據你們的回答和今次事件的結果......我會考慮上書朝廷，嚴肅對待此事。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唔......！", "name": "克洛絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 把夕帶走只是我的判斷，羅德島也不過是接受了我的私人委託而已，這樣的答案滿意嗎？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不滿意。你們十二人任何一次會晤、通信、交談都是牽扯司歲台神經的大事，你怎會不知道？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哦，年紀輕輕，口氣倒是挺老成......", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 司歲台現在的老大是誰？我認得不？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......你遊手好閒太久，人間已變了幾個模樣。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#7$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可惜。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 夕在哪裡？令又在哪裡？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#9$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你們三人相聚尚蜀，又打算做什麼？這隻酒盞......又隱藏了什麼秘密？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 酒盞明明是你們托人從龍門送來的，怎麼還怪起我們來了？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你知道司歲台必須把它握在手裡的意義——", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ——當然，這其中可是拘押著我那好二哥的部分意識的。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......你很清楚。那就很難說幾位都是不知者無罪了。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我可沒打算裝什麼不知者......雖然梁洵確實什麼都沒告訴我。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......哈哈，事到如今我說羅德島什麼都不知道會不會有點牽強？", "name": "克洛絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那是，畢竟你是受害者。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我嗎？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我也是剛剛才意識到的。反倒是你們司歲台啊，一群閒著沒事的琢磨了這麼多年，還琢磨不出嗎？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 巨獸不僅能將自己分離成擁有獨立人格的代理人，也能將自己的意識存儲在一些媒介中苟且偷生......", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......但是你們代理人原來還能再做一次同樣的事情嗎？就像烏薩斯套娃一樣。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#9$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我也不知道我們能不能啊......說不定是他新琢磨出來的吧。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 為了湊齊一百八十一顆黑子之類的。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#2$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......他不會瘋掉嗎？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#7$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他不是已經瘋掉了嗎。就關押在京城，你們又不是見不到他。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 與他見面，是莫大的禁忌。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 司歲台都做了這麼多事，還在乎這？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 夕呢？你找夕做什麼？找了夕還來這裡，又為了什麼？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......我有一個想法。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 根據記載，你總是有很多想法。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯......你倒是挺瞭解我？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （看向這邊了......）", "name": "克洛絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_1021_kroos2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我想......", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......想辦法幹掉那個玩意。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g06_mountainroad_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雨。"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "細密的春雨。"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "character", "